---
title: Double Beef Rump & Garlic-Pepper Butter with Almond Veggies & Mash
description: Simple and sensational – they're the buzzwords for tonight's dinner. A tender cut of beef rump with a punchy fragrant butter,
cooked with garlic and peppercorns, fluffy mash and nutty veggies combine to make a special meal that'll have you buzzing too!

*We’ve replaced the asparagus and carrot in this recipe with broccoli and baby rainbow carrots due to local ingredient
availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
